{"tid":2319003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的...我老豆見到我粒震蛋","createTime":"2020-12-09T19:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T06:06:05.000Z","uid":322094,"like":7,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c88209d449abddf966c2be8145a277553b84fea1","tid":2319003,"uid":322094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T19:24:22.000Z","msg":"話說我將粒震蛋好好保存喺個盒到<br />\n然後再放落個櫃桶度 用啲衫遮住佢<br />\n今日一睇 <br />\n老竇幫我換咗季<br />\n連裝住震蛋嗰個盒都揼咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得返粒蛋同遙控赤裸裸咁係堆衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前佢屎忽痕幫我洗衫已經見到我啲開檔底褲同黑絲<br />\n而家又搵到粒震蛋<br />\n我依家尷尬到想搵個窿埋咗自己<br />\n我平時同男朋友玩咩都比佢知道晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我屌⋯⋯<br />\n到底我而家應該要點面對佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 平時唔係同老竇一齊住，又點估到佢咁得閒幫我執衫同洗衫呀呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea19b2b54d4694fc5ee5f7889807306e5e7fedb","tid":2319003,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T19:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251e21edfaa352f89cdd768818fd1878beb6e909","tid":2319003,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T19:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔住呀女，我J 左"},{"pid":"a9a8ba28087cd092f0fefe97b6c4886c22892409","tid":2319003,"uid":322094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7ea19b2b54d4694fc5ee5f7889807306e5e7fedb","tid":2319003,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T19:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T19:27:39.000Z","msg":"咁你點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f6f98494fd1c3fe907ad55c3b2f46930cdfbaa","tid":2319003,"uid":128102,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score